room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped!" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description: You don’t remember much about what happened.  All you know is that you woke up in some strange and creepy place.  Others have been here before.  Possibly lots of others.  Will your fate be the same as theirs?  You are not willing to wait around to find out!  Can you find your way out of the kidnapper’s lair before he returns or will you suffer the same fate as those who were here before you?
